header.gameNote: BIG TEN BASKETBALL: A SONIC BLOCKBUSTER

videos.description: Maryland scores its first field goal of the game on Jalen Smith's 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Morsell kicks it to Jalen Smith for the triple

videos.description: Chol Marial slaps a shot against the backboard and Maryland takes advantage the other way on a Serrel Smith Jr. trey.

videos.headline: Marial's block sets up Serrel Smith Jr.'s 3

videos.description: Eric Ayala gets inside and gets the layup to go plus the foul on Ohio State's Alonzo Gaffney.
